name: Crowned Heads - Four Kicks Mule Kick LE - 2025
brand: Crowned Heads, Four Kicks Mule Kick LE
additionalNotes: This full-strength toro has a spicy, smokey, and sweetness profile. Its muscular, ebony, oily Mexican San Andres maduro wrapper covers a binder and filler made of Nicaraguan tobaccos. It is the sixth release by this sought after brand, and it marks the first time the Mule Kick LE has been offered with a maduro wrapper. Like its predecessors, the Crowned Heads Four Kicks Mule Kick LE 2022 is handmade at the Tabacalera La Alianza S.A. in the Dominican Republic.Â
